sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Local as Local Network
    participant Test as Testnet
    participant Main as Mainnet
    participant Verify as Etherscan
    participant Monitor as Monitoring
    
    Note over Dev,Monitor: Complete Deployment Flow
    
    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Dev,Local: 1. Local Development
        Dev->>Dev: Configure .env
        Dev->>Dev: npm install
        Dev->>Local: npm run compile
        Local-->>Dev: Compilation success
        Dev->>Local: npm run test
        Local-->>Dev: All tests passing
        Dev->>Local: npm run deploy:local
        Local-->>Dev: Local addresses
    end
    
    rect rgb(232, 240, 254)
        Note over Dev,Test: 2. Testnet Deployment
        Dev->>Dev: Get testnet ETH
        Dev->>Dev: Update .env for testnet
        Dev->>Test: npm run deploy:testnet
        Test-->>Dev: Transaction pending
        Test-->>Dev: Contracts deployed
        Dev->>Test: Set up roles
        Test-->>Dev: Roles configured
        Dev->>Verify: npm run verify:testnet
        Verify-->>Dev: Contracts verified
    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Dev,Test: 3. Integration Testing
        Dev->>Test: Deploy example contracts
        Dev->>Test: Test integrations
        Test-->>Dev: Integration successful
        Dev->>Test: Performance testing
        Test-->>Dev: Gas usage acceptable
    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 235, 238)
        Note over Dev,Main: 4. Mainnet Deployment
        Dev->>Dev: Security audit
        Dev->>Dev: Team approval
        Dev->>Main: npm run deploy:mainnet:dry
        Main-->>Dev: Dry run successful
        Dev->>Main: npm run deploy:mainnet
        Main-->>Dev: Contracts live
        Dev->>Verify: npm run verify:mainnet
        Verify-->>Dev: Verified on Etherscan
    end
    
    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over Dev,Monitor: 5. Post-Deployment
        Dev->>Main: Configure roles
        Dev->>Main: Register initial servers
        Dev->>Monitor: Set up monitoring
        Monitor-->>Dev: Events streaming
        Dev->>Dev: Document addresses
        Dev->>Dev: Update frontend config
    end